### 수강 신청 (PENDING 생성)
POST http://localhost:8080/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 2

{
  "courseId": 1
}

###

### 수강 신청 - OPEN이 아닌 강의 신청 (실패)
POST http://localhost:8080/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 2

{
  "courseId": 2
}

###

### 수강 신청 - 중복 신청 (실패)
POST http://localhost:8080/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 2

{
  "courseId": 1
}

###

### 결제 확정 (PENDING → CONFIRMED)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/confirm
X-User-Id: 2

###

### 결제 확정 - 본인 아닌 경우 (실패)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/confirm
X-User-Id: 999

###

### 수강 취소
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/cancel
X-User-Id: 2

###

### 수강 취소 - 본인 아닌 경우 (실패)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/enrollments/1/cancel
X-User-Id: 999

###

### 내 수강 신청 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/enrollments/me
X-User-Id: 2